properties.name: The Pursuit of Chill
properties.description:
The Passage has never really been known as a "chill ride." We've tried, in various ways, but we're just no good at chilling. We believe that we can change, however, when circumstances call for it. Like right now  because it's hot out, you see  we feel that a certain amount of chill would do us good. We cannot promise that we, ourselves, will be "chilling," but we will at least be seeking out the spots that we believe provide an optimal amount of chill. Baby steps. Baby steps.
